<li class='cover' id='bookCover_39720092'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/39720092-the-adults"><img alt="The Adults" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1522884903l/39720092._SX98_.jpg" />
